reviews.text: Spicy tsekemen which you can order level 0 to 200
Used to be a great place for late night after drinks drinks, still ok but losing an edge on every front.  😔 SAD
Food's good! Nice place to chill and highballs too.

The Tsukemen (dipping noodles) was really terrible. It felt like chewing rubber band. Basically I do not recommend any ramen by this shop. The oysters used to be so good last year. Now it is just in average. The only good is deep fried chicken they can maintain the same quality.
Taste very like the Ramen shop with the same name in Japan    Cold dipping noodle is the best

result.name: 廣島沾麵本舖爆彈屋

reviews.text: 店長さんはやる気が無いながら、やめ方がいいじゃない？
Spicy tsekemen which you can order level 0 to 200
食物環境不錯，地方較細，好大機會需要等位。辣度最高有200倍，喜歡挑戰的可以一試

食過真正嘅廣島沾麵，就會覺得呢度只係形似，感覺同超市買嘅沾麵即食麵都冇乜太大分別， 係多咗啲青瓜絲椰菜絲同三片冇乜味嘅肉。 各方面只係不過不失，聊以慰藉還可以嘅。
Btw，雖然我都明白樓上鋪可能經營唔容易， 但係整體有啲感覺唔大方，例如：晚市規定要消費滿150蚊/人，仲有食辣嘅沾麵竟然都唔免費提供冰水 🙄
